    "content" : "<div class=\"quotetitle\">\n Nik wrote:\n</div>\n<div class=\"quotecontent\">\n Getting stuck in there Steve, nice one \n <img src=\"./images/smilies/icon_wink.gif\" alt=\":wink:\" title=\"Wink\"> \n <br>\n <br>The 59 would have had thick lip dog legs (mine's late December '59 and has factory thick lips)\n <br>\n <br>In fact my 62 crossover split had thick lips too, so yours is squarely in the right range for these.\n <br>\n <br>Hope this helps mate.\n <br>\n <br>Cheers.\n <br>\n <br>Nik \n <img src=\"./images/smilies/icon_biggrin.gif\" alt=\":D\" title=\"Big Grin\">\n</div>\n<br>\n<br>Hi Nik,\n<br>\n<br>Thanks for that, as we expected,\n<br>\n<br>Thick lips rule \n<img src=\"./images/smilies/icon_wink.gif\" alt=\":wink:\" title=\"Wink\"> \n<br>\n<br>Steve",
